  "title": "Pan Seared Moroccan Chicken Liver Skewers",
  "description": "A funky and snappy Moroccan dish featuring chicken liver, perfect for a quick fix and high in protein, this recipe is a deep fry alternative with a twist of Moroccan spices.",
