  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a skillet over medium high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, ginger, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken liver pieces to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated chicken liver pieces onto skewers.",
    "Add the skewers to the preheated skillet and cook for 5 minutes per side.",
    "Remove the skewers from the skillet and garnish with parsley.",
    "Serve the skewers hot with your choice of sides.",
    "Let the skewers rest for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley if desired."
